body:
Welcome to my GitHub page!

I shall mainly use this for hosting some of my JS projects.


###Projects

* [Math-to-LaTeX converter](http://manishearth.github.com/MathToTex/MathToTeX.html): This takes typed math as input. and converts it to LaTeX. By typed math, I mean stuff like `(kq_1q_2)/(r^2)`--eg no special LaTeX markup.
* [8085 Op Code Generator](http://manishearth.github.com/OpcodeGen.html): Compiles 8085 programs.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
